+-------------------------------------+---------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| Name                                | Description                                                                     | 
+=====================================+=================================================================================+
| :method:`db.currentOp()`            | Reports the current in-progress operations.                                     |
+-------------------------------------+---------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| :method:`db.killOp()`               | Terminates a specified operation.                                               |
+-------------------------------------+---------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| :method:`db.printCollectionStats()` | Prints statistics from every collection. Wraps :method:`db.collection.stats()`. |
+-------------------------------------+---------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
